hoes off or shoes on?—to how to make extra seating out of every surface of my apartment. In this installment, I’ll show you how to gather your friends even when it’s freezing outside and no one wants to leave the house. Got company? \u003ca href=\"https://food52.attn.tv/p/HBo/comeonover\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSign up here\u003c/a\u003e for my emails.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003chr/\u003e\n\n              \u003cp\u003eOn Sunday in Brooklyn, the forecast predicted snow. Also on my personal forecast? A dinner party at our apartment with all of our friends. I was worried the weather would inspire a digital blizzard of “Sorry, can’t make it!” texts, but, minus one friend with a cold, everyone stopped by. Here’s what I served to lure everyone from their warm nests and into mine.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n              \n\n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ca href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button\" data-pin-do=\"buttonPin\" data-pin-media=\"\" data-pin-custom=\"true\" data-ga-event=\"inPageInteraction\" data-ga-event-action=\"Pinterest Share\" data-ga-event-label=\"Article Body Image\" data-ga-destination-url=\"none\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16.9 20.8\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16.8 6.3C16.5 3.2 13.6.4 10.1.1 4.8-.5.1 2.7 0 7.9c0 2.4.8 4 2.9 4.8 1.5-1.5-.3-2.4-.5-4C2 4.3 7.1.1 11.7 2.9c3.2 1.9 2.6 9.9-1.2 10.7-.8.1-1.8-.1-2.1-.5-1.9-1.8 1.5-4.8.4-7.3-.9-2.1-3.6-.4-3.9 1.5-.2 1 .3 2 .3 2.9 0 2.1-1.3 5-1.7 7.1-.2.9-.3 2.6-.1 3.4h1.5c1-1.6 1.6-4.1 2.1-6.3.3-.2.5.4.7.6 1.8 1.4 5 .6 6.4-.7 2.1-1.7 3-5.2 2.7-8\" fill=\"currentColor\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n      \u003c/a\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 1400px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/venDmR_pUOy7dQoZEnQBrEaUL5Q=/778x775/filters:forma